description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=1/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Evolve or die! You are a tiny cell floating around somewhere in the universe. You will have to evolve and add cells to your original cell. BUT!!! Watch out for evil bosses and nasty viruses.
